    "body": "This informational BIP provides a set of terminology to refer to the various components, scripts, and concepts used to compose Bitcoin transactions.\r\n\r\nThis proposal was [discussed](https://gnusha.org/pi/bitcoindev/6bb373cc-bee0-13a3-a510-b65d4faa867f@murch.one/) in 2023 on the mailing list and had subsequently been reviewed and developed against [my personal BIPs repository](https://github.com/murchandamus/bips/pull/1). I recently picked it up again to address the outstanding review and would now like to put it forth for broader consideration.",
